WEBVTT

00:00:00.040 --> 00:00:14.740
( Watch on Kissasia.vip )

00:01:25.280 --> 00:01:25.960
Speak.

00:01:26.800 --> 00:01:29.130
At the entrance of the Harmonica Society,

00:01:29.320 --> 00:01:30.920
holding an open-air concert

00:01:31.480 --> 00:01:34.810
to incite anti-Manchurian and anti-Japanese sentiments.

00:01:35.080 --> 00:01:36.800
At the broadcasting station,

00:01:37.320 --> 00:01:39.000
playing 'The Pioneers'

00:01:39.759 --> 00:01:42.000
with a hint of violence.

00:01:42.360 --> 00:01:43.240
Great.

00:01:44.039 --> 00:01:45.300
Who is the mastermind?

00:01:46.120 --> 00:01:47.039
Is it Qin Na?

00:01:47.880 --> 00:01:49.610
Don't make false accusations.

00:01:50.720 --> 00:01:52.450
It has nothing to do with Qin Na.

00:01:52.960 --> 00:01:54.000
I organized it.

00:01:55.320 --> 00:01:56.280
I did it.

00:01:59.000 --> 00:01:59.840
Bastard!

00:02:00.360 --> 00:02:02.040
Come at me if you have the guts.

00:02:08.120 --> 00:02:09.759
It seems the intensity isn't enough.

00:02:09.759 --> 00:02:10.889
We need to step it up.

00:02:13.600 --> 00:02:14.400
Gu Xiaoxiong,

00:02:15.120 --> 00:02:17.160
a wise man submits to circumstances.

00:02:17.160 --> 00:02:18.360
Why suffer like this?

00:02:22.079 --> 00:02:22.800
Chief.

00:02:23.240 --> 00:02:24.680
Gu Xiaoxiong is an educated man.

00:02:24.680 --> 00:02:26.480
Maybe reasoning with him is more effective.

00:02:26.480 --> 00:02:27.079
Let me try.

00:02:27.079 --> 00:02:28.280
You traitor!

00:02:29.079 --> 00:02:31.010
Stop pretending to be the good guy.

00:02:31.520 --> 00:02:33.960
One day you will all die a horrible death.

00:02:38.120 --> 00:02:39.000
Old Chen,

00:02:39.240 --> 00:02:40.560
you are still too kind.

00:02:41.040 --> 00:02:42.640
Too soft-hearted, you know?

00:02:42.760 --> 00:02:44.720
You can't be gentle with this kind of person.

00:02:44.720 --> 00:02:45.850
We have to use force.

00:02:46.120 --> 00:02:46.960
Leave it to me.

00:03:15.600 --> 00:03:16.660
What are you doing?

00:03:17.040 --> 00:03:17.880
Let me go!

00:03:18.040 --> 00:03:19.360
Don't move! Let me go!

00:03:30.960 --> 00:03:32.890
You play the harmonica quite well.

00:03:33.720 --> 00:03:35.380
Then you just need your mouth.

00:03:36.000 --> 00:03:37.329
Your hands are useless.

00:03:46.440 --> 00:03:47.240
Miss Qin.

00:03:49.440 --> 00:03:50.320
I didn't expect

00:03:50.840 --> 00:03:52.760
we'd meet again like this.

00:03:53.400 --> 00:03:54.460
Please have a seat.

00:03:54.640 --> 00:03:55.840
No need, Mr. Matsuda.

00:03:56.960 --> 00:03:58.220
Where is Gu Xiaoxiong?

00:03:58.680 --> 00:03:59.520
I heard

00:04:00.120 --> 00:04:01.640
you brought him here.

00:04:02.240 --> 00:04:04.440
My harmonica society still has classes tomorrow.

00:04:04.440 --> 00:04:05.600
Can I take him back?

00:04:07.280 --> 00:04:09.000
The members are all very scared,

00:04:09.000 --> 00:04:10.530
not knowing what happened.

00:04:10.800 --> 00:04:12.920
Your harmonica team captain

00:04:13.360 --> 00:04:14.600
was at the broadcasting station,

00:04:14.600 --> 00:04:16.130
conducting 'The Pioneers'

00:04:16.519 --> 00:04:19.320
to incite the people against Manchuria and Japan.

00:04:23.880 --> 00:04:24.800
Mr. Matsuda.

00:04:25.600 --> 00:04:27.530
Is there a misunderstanding here?

00:04:28.480 --> 00:04:29.480
He is still young.

00:04:29.880 --> 00:04:31.880
He couldn't possibly do such a thing.

00:04:31.880 --> 00:04:33.360
If there is any offense,

00:04:33.760 --> 00:04:34.890
please forgive him.

00:04:39.120 --> 00:04:40.159
Can I see him?

00:04:40.960 --> 00:04:41.760
Of course.

00:04:42.120 --> 00:04:43.480
I will give them a call.

00:04:54.400 --> 00:04:55.760
Tell Section Chief Qian,

00:04:55.760 --> 00:04:57.400
I will bring Miss Qin immediately

00:04:57.400 --> 00:04:59.000
to see Mr. Gu Xiaoxiong.

00:04:59.400 --> 00:05:00.930
Please ask them to prepare.

00:05:10.280 --> 00:05:11.280
Captain Matsuda.

00:05:18.880 --> 00:05:19.640
Bastard!

00:05:21.480 --> 00:05:22.160
Yes.

00:05:40.480 --> 00:05:43.320
They are too ruthless.

00:05:44.000 --> 00:05:44.720
Miss Qin.

00:05:45.560 --> 00:05:46.760
Please persuade him.

00:05:47.120 --> 00:05:48.240
If this continues,

00:05:48.600 --> 00:05:50.720
I'm afraid Mr. Gu's hands

00:05:51.840 --> 00:05:53.970
won't even be able to hold a harmonica.

00:05:54.800 --> 00:05:56.200
Just admit your mistake,

00:05:57.040 --> 00:05:58.840
and sign a letter of repentance.

00:05:59.360 --> 00:06:01.120
I promise that he and those children

00:06:01.120 --> 00:06:02.320
can all get lenient sentences.

00:06:02.320 --> 00:06:03.840
I promise.

00:06:08.080 --> 00:06:09.880
Can I have a word with him?

00:06:10.360 --> 00:06:11.000
Sure.

00:06:37.040 --> 00:06:37.800
Xiaoxiong.

00:06:45.600 --> 00:06:46.320
Xiaoxiong.

00:06:56.520 --> 00:06:57.400
Sister Qin.

00:06:58.880 --> 00:06:59.840
Sister Qin.

00:07:15.040 --> 00:07:16.200
Sorry, Sister Qin.

00:07:18.480 --> 00:07:19.540
I got you involved.

00:07:23.600 --> 00:07:25.200
I have nothing to confess.

00:07:30.680 --> 00:07:31.400
Xiaoxiong.

00:07:32.000 --> 00:07:32.520
Xiaoxiong.

00:07:32.520 --> 00:07:33.200
Miss Qin.

00:07:33.520 --> 00:07:35.080
Are you crazy?

00:07:40.240 --> 00:07:41.000
Xiaoxiong.

00:07:41.120 --> 00:07:42.159
Send Miss Qin

00:07:42.560 --> 00:07:43.240
Xiaoxiong.

00:07:43.320 --> 00:07:43.840
away.

00:07:43.920 --> 00:07:44.880
Miss Qin, rest assured.

00:07:44.880 --> 00:07:46.480
Captain Matsuda will handle it.

00:07:46.480 --> 00:07:47.159
Go.

00:07:50.080 --> 00:07:51.140
Mr. Gu, have a seat.

00:07:51.680 --> 00:07:53.120
Miss Qin, I'm sorry.

00:07:53.280 --> 00:07:54.760
Mr. Gu, why are you doing this?

00:07:54.760 --> 00:07:55.880
Mr. Gu. Mr. Gu.

00:08:39.760 --> 00:08:41.159
Why are you following me?

00:08:42.120 --> 00:08:42.840
No.

00:08:44.720 --> 00:08:45.960
Did Captain Matsuda

00:08:46.240 --> 00:08:47.440
ask you to follow me?

00:08:47.760 --> 00:08:48.920
No.

00:08:49.600 --> 00:08:51.480
Captain Matsuda asked me to safely escort Miss Qin

00:08:51.480 --> 00:08:52.480
home.

00:08:54.480 --> 00:08:55.200
Thank you.

00:08:56.120 --> 00:08:57.040
Miss Qin, wait.

00:08:58.480 --> 00:09:00.610
I've been wondering about something.

00:09:01.120 --> 00:09:02.320
How could there be anti-Japanese and anti-Manchukuo elements

00:09:02.320 --> 00:09:03.240
in the harmonica club

00:09:03.240 --> 00:09:04.900
when Miss Qin is so beautiful?

00:09:07.000 --> 00:09:08.000
Nonsense.

00:09:08.720 --> 00:09:09.880
Believe it or not, I'll take you to Captain Matsuda right now

00:09:09.880 --> 00:09:11.210
and we'll confront him.

00:09:11.320 --> 00:09:12.400
Face to face.

00:09:13.800 --> 00:09:14.560
Don't.

00:09:15.360 --> 00:09:16.480
I just want to ask

00:09:17.200 --> 00:09:19.000
if I can join the harmonica club?

00:09:19.360 --> 00:09:20.640
I like music too.

00:09:22.000 --> 00:09:22.760
Rascal.

00:09:23.160 --> 00:09:23.720
Miss Qin.

00:09:23.880 --> 00:09:25.010
I haven't finished.

00:09:25.120 --> 00:09:26.200
Let's talk.

00:09:31.320 --> 00:09:32.040
Go.

00:09:35.560 --> 00:09:36.720
Sister Qin, get in.

00:09:37.680 --> 00:09:38.400
Let's go together.

00:09:38.400 --> 00:09:39.130
You go first.

00:10:03.120 --> 00:10:05.120
This is Comrade Dajiang's latest intel.

00:10:05.120 --> 00:10:06.450
It must be sent tonight.

00:10:10.200 --> 00:10:11.640
You can't send telegrams anymore.

00:10:11.640 --> 00:10:13.440
Gu Xiaoxiong is just a scholar.

00:10:14.000 --> 00:10:16.060
He can't stand the Japanese torture.

00:10:16.320 --> 00:10:18.080
Besides, the Japanese already suspect you.

00:10:18.080 --> 00:10:18.810
Can't you see

00:10:18.840 --> 00:10:20.300
someone is following you?

00:10:20.840 --> 00:10:22.840
You must leave Harbin immediately.

00:10:23.040 --> 00:10:25.100
I'll send you out of the city tonight.

00:10:26.960 --> 00:10:28.760
Xiaoxiong didn't say anything.

00:10:29.960 --> 00:10:30.760
It's just that

00:10:31.720 --> 00:10:34.320
he won't be able to play the harmonica anymore.

00:10:40.560 --> 00:10:41.360
I won't leave.

00:10:42.160 --> 00:10:43.920
Xiaoxiong and the other team members

00:10:43.920 --> 00:10:44.720
must be saved.

00:10:45.640 --> 00:10:48.560
The transmitter in the warehouse can't be installed for nothing.

00:10:48.560 --> 00:10:49.440
Sister Qin.

00:11:17.600 --> 00:11:18.600
As agreed, at 9:30

00:11:18.760 --> 00:11:22.090
the radio and transmitter will be turned on at the same time.

00:12:04.520 --> 00:12:05.520
How is Xiaoxiong?

00:12:06.520 --> 00:12:07.280
He's fine.

00:12:07.840 --> 00:12:09.570
Hurry up and send the telegram.

00:12:10.000 --> 00:12:12.000
This is the intel Xiaoling just got.

00:12:14.320 --> 00:12:15.720
I'll translate it first.

00:12:18.120 --> 00:12:19.180
At the agreed 9:30,

00:12:19.640 --> 00:12:20.640
Lao Zhang's transmitter

00:12:20.640 --> 00:12:22.900
and our radio will start at the same time.

00:12:50.040 --> 00:12:51.400
These bastards.

00:12:52.200 --> 00:12:53.040
They are trying to surround

00:12:53.040 --> 00:12:55.640
the Anti-Japanese United Army recon squad at Mao'er Mountain.

00:12:55.640 --> 00:12:56.800
The recon squad has already finished

00:12:56.800 --> 00:12:59.440
scouting the exact location of the Japanese Dong'an armory

00:12:59.440 --> 00:13:01.520
and the guards' shift change times.

00:13:01.720 --> 00:13:03.080
So the most important thing right now

00:13:03.080 --> 00:13:04.840
is to have the squad evacuate quickly

00:13:04.840 --> 00:13:06.100
and pass the intel out.

00:13:06.920 --> 00:13:08.250
I've been to that place.

00:13:08.560 --> 00:13:09.640
We can have the squad

00:13:09.640 --> 00:13:11.600
evacuate by detouring to the rocky slope on the west.

00:13:11.600 --> 00:13:13.600
That's a blind spot for the cavalry.

00:13:13.640 --> 00:13:15.080
We only have three minutes.

00:13:15.080 --> 00:13:16.520
If the telegram isn't finished,

00:13:16.520 --> 00:13:18.920
transfer to transmission point 3 immediately.

00:13:18.920 --> 00:13:20.580
You transmit. I'll cover you.

00:13:36.760 --> 00:13:37.560
Time's up.

00:13:47.520 --> 00:13:48.240
There's a signal.